24#include <sys/cdefs.h>
25#ifndef lint
26__RCSID("$NetBSD: print-ah.c,v 1.6 2017/02/05 04:05:05 spz Exp $");
27#endif
28
29/* \summary: IPSEC Authentication Header printer */
30
31#ifdef HAVE_CONFIG_H
32#include "config.h"
33#endif
34
35#include <netdissect-stdinc.h>
36
37#include "ah.h"
38
39#include "netdissect.h"
40#include "extract.h"
41
42int
43ah_print(netdissect_options *ndo, register const u_char *bp)
44{
45 register const struct ah *ah;
46 int sumlen;
47
48 ah = (const struct ah *)bp;
49
50 ND_TCHECK(*ah);
51
52 sumlen = ah->ah_len << 2;
53
54 ND_PRINT((ndo, "AH(spi=0x%08x", EXTRACT_32BITS(&ah->ah_spi)));
55 if (ndo->ndo_vflag)
56 ND_PRINT((ndo, ",sumlen=%d", sumlen));
57 ND_TCHECK_32BITS(ah + 1);
58 ND_PRINT((ndo, ",seq=0x%x", EXTRACT_32BITS(ah + 1)));
59 if (!ND_TTEST2(*bp, sizeof(struct ah) + sumlen)) {
60 ND_PRINT((ndo, "[truncated]):"));
61 return -1;
62 }
63 ND_PRINT((ndo, "): "));
64
65 return sizeof(struct ah) + sumlen;
66 trunc:
67 ND_PRINT((ndo, "[|AH]"));
68 return -1;
69}
